# Contributing

1. Sign the [Contribution Agreement][contribution agreement], which just lets
   us assure customers that they can use the code we provide them without
   worry.
2. [Submit a PR][gh-pr-docs] against this repository.
3. If accepted, the maintainers will update our private fork, push the update
   to the master branch of this repository, close your PR, and then upload
   signed jars to [jcenter][bintray-respository], [maven central][maven], and
   [sonatype][sonatype] artifact repositories.

[contribution agreement]: http://docs.urbanairship.com/contribution-agreement.html
[gh-pr-docs]: https://help.github.com/articles/using-pull-requests/
[bintray-repository]: https://bintray.com/bintray/jcenter
[maven-central]: http://search.maven.org/
[sonatype]: https://oss.sonatype.org/

